           <section class="full-width-content text-content dark-row no-padding-bottom background-no-repeat" style="background-image:url(https://docrdsfx76ssb.cloudfront.net/static/1720612332/pages/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/stars-effects.svg);background-color:#031f39"> 
            <div class="grid-container"> 
             <div class="inner-content grid-x grid-margin-x grid-padding-x"> 
              <div class="cell"> 
               <h3 class="h1" style="text-align: center; color: #ff950a;">More than a link shortener</h3> 
               <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; font-weight: 400; text-wrap: balance; color: #fffdf8;">Knowing how your clicks and scans are performing should be as easy as making them. Track, analyze, and optimize all your connections in one place.</p> 
               <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px;"><a class="btn btn-secondary btn-secondary-dark" href="https://bitly.com/pages/pricing" data-testid="sdet-cta-bottom-button">Get started for free</a></p> 
